@vietnam_seek
title: Seek out informal contacts with the Vietnamese Communist Party, investigating the possibility of further relations.
view-if: vietnam_relations == 0
subtitle: -1 resources
choose-if: resources >= 1
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
on-arrival: resources -= 1; vietnam_relations += 1; left_strength += 2;

It takes a few weeks, but through the North Vietnamese embassy in Stockholm we succeed in arranging a meeting representatives of the VCP. Though initially suspicious due to our membership of NATO, the meeting soon turns cordial as we assure them of our intentions. 

Given their dire situation, the VCP assures us that they would appreciate any help we can provide, diplomatic or material. [? if a_in_government == 0 : Being out of government there is little more we can do at the moment, but i ?][? if a_in_government == 1 : I ?]n the future we will be able to expand on this relationship.


