title: Establish official relations with the Vietnamese Communist Party, in a front to America. 
view-if: vietnam_relations == 1
choose-if: a_in_government == 1
unavailable-subtitle: The Vietnamese Communist Party would rather wait until we are in government.
on-arrival: vietnam_relations += 1; left_strength += 5; left_dissent -= 10; left_worker_dissent -= 7; left_strength += 5; right_worker_dissent += 8; member += 10*efc; a_activity += 0.02;

The meeting is to take place inside the home of [[+ chancellor +]], the press is quick to swarms the entrance as the first handshakes are exchanged. Once inside, cautious smiles are exchanged as the order of business is laid out. 

The hours pass and much is agreed upon. When the meeting concludes, the leader of the delegation stays around for evening coffee, he leaves in a hopeful mood.

